            "title": "Glucan Particles Are a Powerful Adjuvant for the HBsAg, Favoring Antiviral Immunity",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Edna",
                    "lastName": "Soares"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
